headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  HIGGINS, BRIAN J.

snippet: HIGGINS--Brian J.,Born November 22, 1949, died peacefully April 12, 2016. Successful Commercial Real Estate Broker at JLL, Staubach, C&W. Survived by his wife, two children, two grandchildren, six siblings and a large extended family. Visitation Monday, 2-5pm and 7-9pm at Frank E. Campbell Funeral Chapel, 81st St. and Madison Ave. Mass of Christian Burial Tuesday, 10am at Holy Family Church, 315 E.47th St., NYC, NY. Interment at Holy Rood Cemetery, Westbury, NY. 1/3
